OL,3,CMartyn's Law to receive Royal Assent
OL,4,Cafter campaign by Martyn Hett's mother
OL,6,FFigen Murray has welcomed the
OL,7,Fsignificant moment, saying the "much
OL,8,Fneeded" law will secure her son's
OL,9,Flegacy and prevent other families from
OL,10,Fgoing through what she and 21 others
OL,11,Fhad to endure.
OL,13,FFigen, the initiator of Martyn's Law,
OL,14,Fsaid: "Whilst nothing can bring Martyn
OL,15,Fback, this much needed law will secure
OL,16,Fhis legacy and help to prevent more
OL,17,Ffamilies enduring the pain and loss
OL,18,Fthat mine, alongside 21 others, have
OL,19,Fexperienced since the Manchester Arena
OL,20,Fterror attack.
OL,26,@vD@GOU
