OL,3,CMartyn's Law to receive Royal Assent
OL,4,Cafter campaign by Martyn Hett's mother
OL,6,FFigen began campaigning for tougher
OL,7,Fsecurity measures after she went to a
OL,8,Fconcert in Salford 18 months after the
OL,9,FManchester Arena attack.
OL,11,FTo her horror, she realised that no
OL,12,Fsecurity seemed to be in place - the
OL,13,Fsmall bag she was carrying was not
OL,14,Feven checked.
OL,16,FShortly afterwards, Figen decided to
OL,17,Flaunch a government petition calling
OL,18,Ffor "Martyn's Law".
OL,20,FWhat would Martyn's Law mean?
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
