OL,3,CMartyn's Law to receive Royal Assent
OL,4,Cafter campaign by Martyn Hett's mother
OL,6,FThe introduction of Martyn's Law,
OL,7,Fofficially titled the Terrorism
OL,8,F(Protection of Premises) Bill, will
OL,9,Fmake it a legal requirement for public
OL,10,Fplaces to improve security measures.
OL,12,FThose responsible for premises will be
OL,13,Frequired to fulfil necessary but
OL,14,Fproportionate steps, according to
OL,15,Ftheir capacity, to help keep the
OL,16,Fpublic safe.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
