OL,3,CMartyn's Law to receive Royal Assent
OL,4,Cafter campaign by Martyn Hett's mother
OL,6,FThis includes a tiered approach,
OL,7,Flinked to the size of the venue, how
OL,8,Fmany people will be there and the
OL,9,Factivity taking place, making sure
OL,10,Fundue burdens are not placed on small
OL,11,Fbusinesses.
OL,13,FA standard tier premises will apply to
OL,14,Flocations with a capacity of more than
OL,15,F200 people but under 800.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
