OL,3,CMartyn's Law to receive Royal Assent
OL,4,Cafter campaign by Martyn Hett's mother
OL,6,FWill Martyn's law apply to the whole
OL,7,Fof the UK?
OL,9,FThe legislation will apply across
OL,10,FEngland, Wales, Scotland and Northern
OL,11,FIreland, as national security is a
OL,12,Freserved matter for the UK Government.
OL,14,FNick Aldworth, former National
OL,15,FCoordinator for Protect and Prepare at
OL,16,FCounter Terrorism Policing, said: "I'm
OL,17,Fdelighted that this legislation now
OL,18,Fexists, it has been the missing piece
OL,19,Fof the jigsaw that was needed to
OL,20,Fcomplete the UK Counter-Terrorism
OL,21,Fstrategy.
OL,26,@xD@cOU
