OL,3,CMartyn's Law to receive Royal Assent
OL,4,Cafter campaign by Martyn Hett's mother
OL,6,F"I pay tribute to my co-campaigner,
OL,7,FFigen Murray whose resilience and
OL,8,Fdetermination, while dealing with her
OL,9,Fown grief and the needs of her family,
OL,10,Fhas made this all possible.
OL,12,FBrendan Cox, co-founder of Survivors
OL,13,FAgainst Terror, said: "You should
OL,14,Fnever doubt what the courage, bravery
OL,15,Fand passion of a mother can achieve.
OL,17,F"This was never a quest for sympathy,
OL,18,Fit was a desire for change to make us
OL,19,Fall safer. Today Figen has achieved
OL,20,Fthat, and we all owe her a debt of
OL,21,Fthanks.
OL,26,@uD@WOU
