OL,3,CMartyn's Law to receive Royal Assent
OL,4,Cafter campaign by Martyn Hett's mother
OL,6,F"After years of delay the Government
OL,7,Fhas got this on the statute book
OL,8,Fwithin months of coming into office
OL,9,Fand they deserve credit for that.
OL,11,F"I'd also like to thank all the other
OL,12,Fsurvivors of terror attacks who have
OL,13,Fbacked Figen's campaign to get this
OL,14,Flaw implemented. It wouldn't have
OL,15,Fhappened without them."
